snippet.title: Scania accelerates operations across its global workforce with ChatGPT
snippet.description: Scania builds the trucks, buses, and transport systems that keep the world moving. With AI in their engineering-led organisation, they're evolving from vehicle maker to sustainable transport ecosystem leader. Read more: https://openai.com/index/scania/
